Title: Fix LDAP synchronisation of customer attribute
Class: fix
Compatible: incomp
Component: multisite
Date: 1633446646
Edition: cme
Knowledge: doc
Level: 1
State: unknown
Version: 2.1.0b1

The customer attribute of users synchronized by a LDAP connection were always
set to the sites default customer. Now all users will get the customer of the
LDAP connection they are synchronized with.

Please keep in mind that there could be changes on the next synchronization.

